gridworld.actor

Class TextCell

  • java.lang.Object
    • gridworld.actor.Actor
      • gridworld.actor.TextCell

  • public class TextCell
extends Actor
    TextCell is the "Actor pretender" class. It inherits from Actor. Without the minimal TextCellDisplay class, TextCells objects would display as "?".

    TextCells display as black text (from toString) on a white background. All the normal text "options" apply.

    Version:
    Nov 15, 2007
    Author:
    George Peck, TextCell.java
